OL,3,CBoy found guilty of murder of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold Holly Newton
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fthe murder of 15-year-old schoolgirl
OL,8,FHolly Newton.
OL,10,FHolly, who was from Haltwhistle, died
OL,11,Fin hospital after suffering fatal stab
OL,12,Fwounds in Hexham in January 2023.
OL,14,FThe 17-year-old defendant, who cannot
OL,15,Fbe named because of his age, had
OL,16,Fadmitted killing Holly and being in
OL,17,Fpossession of a knife but denied
OL,18,Fmurdering Holly and the unlawful
OL,19,Fwounding of another teenager.
