OL,3,CBoy found guilty of murder of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold Holly Newton
OL,6,FIn court, he claimed he did not intend
OL,7,Fto hurt Holly and had intended to
OL,8,Finstead hurt himself with the knife.
OL,10,FHowever, following a six-week trial at
OL,11,FNewcastle Crown Court, the jury came
OL,12,Fto a verdict of guilty of murder, also
OL,13,Ffinding him guilty of another charge
OL,14,Fof wounding with intent.
OL,16,FThe youth will be sentenced on 31
OL,17,FOctober.
OL,19,FHolly's mum Micala Trussler read a
OL,20,Fstatement aloud about her daughter to
OL,21,Fthe courtroom.
