OL,3,CBoy found guilty of murder of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold Holly Newton
OL,6,FShe said: "Holly was a beautiful
OL,7,Fchild. She was my firstborn, a clingy
OL,8,Fchild who never left my side. She grew
OL,9,Finto a funny and happy teenager who
OL,10,Fwould do anything for anyone."
OL,12,FShe added: "She fell in love with
OL,13,Fdancing, it gave her an opportunity to
OL,14,Fexpress herself and helped her self
OL,15,Fconfidence enormously, it genuinely
OL,16,Fmade her feel fearless."
