OL,3,CBoy found guilty of murder of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold Holly Newton
OL,6,FShe also read a statement outside
OL,7,FCourt, saying: "As a family, it has
OL,8,Fbeen extremely painful to have to sit
OL,9,Fthrough a lengthy trial and reach this
OL,10,Fpoint. To think that Holly should have
OL,11,Fbeen getting her GCSE results last
OL,12,Fweek but instead, our baby girl's
OL,13,Ffuture was cruelly taken away from us.
OL,15,F"We are grateful to the many people
OL,16,Fwho have shown their support as we
OL,17,Fcontinue to navigate a life without
OL,18,FHolly in it."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
