OL,6,F"Thanks to their hard work and
OL,7,Fdedication, as well as continued
OL,8,Fsupport from the local community, the
OL,9,Fweight of evidence against the
OL,10,Foffender was so overwhelming that a
OL,11,Fjury has found him guilty of all
OL,12,Fcharges
OL,14,F"His life and those of his loved one
OL,15,Fhave also been changed forever by the
OL,16,Fdecisions he made that night.
OL,18,F"Violence has absolutely no place in
OL,19,Fsociety ` and as a Force we are
OL,20,Fcommitted to working with our partners
OL,21,Fto tackle such offending.
