OL,6,F"However, each and every one of us has
OL,7,Fa role to play ` and we must all come
OL,8,Ftogether to help prevent violence and
OL,9,Fknife crime.
OL,11,F"This includes continuing to educate
OL,12,Four young people and talking to them
OL,13,Fabout the pain and suffering caused by
OL,14,Fviolence."
