OL,6,FFollowing the verdict, Lynsey Colling,
OL,7,FHead of the Crown Court Unit for CPS
OL,8,FNorth East, said: "The killing of
OL,9,FHolly Newton has been utterly
OL,10,Fdevastating for her family and our
OL,11,Ffocus throughout this case has been to
OL,12,Fensure that the person responsible was
OL,13,Fbrought to justice for his actions.
