OL,3,CBoy found guilty of murder of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold Holly Newton
OL,6,F"A significant challenge for us in the
OL,7,Fearly stages of the case was to
OL,8,Festablish the defendant's fitness to
OL,9,Fplead, which had been raised as an
OL,10,Fissue by the defence. The Crown
OL,11,Finstructed specialist psychologists,
OL,12,Fwhose independent assessments
OL,13,Fpersuaded the court that the defendant
OL,14,Fdid, in fact, have the capacity to
OL,15,Fenter pleas and to stand trial for the
OL,16,Fallegations made against him"
