OL,6,F"Today's outcome is the result of
OL,7,Feffective partnership working between
OL,8,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service and
OL,9,FNorthumbria Police from the very early
OL,10,Fstages of this investigation.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with Holly's
OL,13,Ffamily, for whom this remains a
OL,14,Fparticularly difficult time, and we
OL,15,Fonly hope that Holly's family can take
OL,16,Fsome measure of comfort in seeing her
OL,17,Fkiller brought to justice."
